General.Name: Capitol Health Ltd
General.Description: Capitol Health Limited provides diagnostic imaging modalities and related services to the healthcare market in Australia. It offers a range of diagnostic imaging services, including general x-ray, magnetic resonance imaging, ultrasound, mammography, Doppler, orthopantomogram, echocardiography, computed tomography, CT angiography, cone beam CT, nuclear medicine, bone densitometry, and fluoroscopy. It operated various clinics in Victoria, Tasmania, Western Australia, and South Australia under the Capital Radiology brand, as well as under the Imaging Olympic Park, Radiology Tasmania, Fowler Simmons Radiology, Womens' Imaging, Direct Radiology, and Future Medical Imaging Group brand names. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in East Melbourne, Australia.
